&lt;p&gt;(Quote from the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/alvarogarcia7/base-bdd-cucumber/blob/master/README.md&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;README.md&lt;/a&gt;):&lt;/p&gt;

